data.description: Fixer, Fixer, Fixer! Investors or Handy homeowners! Looking for a complete remodel/overhaul to realize the full potential of this home. Priced to procure bids and sell quickly. Two-story townhome unit in the popular Smoketree Community. Popular Functional floorplan with two master suites upstairs. Downstairs a large living room with full volume ceilings, dining room and step saver kitchen. Direct  access two car garage. This home offers a very generous rear patio yard with many possibilities. Quiet location walkable to the community pool, spa and clubhouse.  There is plenty of guest parking close to the townhome. Smoke tree is a quaint community of 125 townhomes in the heart of Lake Forest just minutes away from shopping centers, Irvine Spectrum, Lake Forest Sports Park, and the Great Park with hiking and Nature trails. Walking distance to Serrano Highlands parks and recreation, community pool and spa. Easy access to the 5 and 405 freeway and the 241 toll road.
